%% C4 Context Diagram — Foundry Orchestration Composer
flowchart TB
    operator["Operator
(platform / engineering)"]
    repo["Repo Native Authorities
personas, skills, roles, runbooks, templates, model routing"]
    runtimes["Runtime Adapters
simulation / terminal / future real executors"]
    models["Model Providers / Gateways
existing Foundry routing"]
    evidence["Continuity + Evidence Authorities
continuity state, approvals, evidence bundle targets"]

    subgraph foundry["Flagship Foundry System"]
        companion["Cursor Companion
canonical write surface"]
        composer["Orchestration Composer
compose + pipeline + review"]
        control["Control Plane + Composer APIs
validate, persist, compile, execute"]
        graph["Graph / Viewer Projection
read-only topology + blast radius"]
        registry["Building Block Registry Projection"]
    end

    operator -->|browse, compose, approve, launch| companion
    companion --> composer
    companion --> graph
    composer -->|save/read declared artifacts| control
    control -->|project blocks| registry
    registry -->|read only| repo
    control -->|compile to draft work orders / approved plans| evidence
    control -->|launch approved runs only| runtimes
    runtimes -->|status + logs + telemetry refs| evidence
    control -->|session projection| companion
    control -->|topology + run overlays| graph
    runtimes --> models
